"{\"uid\": \"dailycaller.com-2024-07-26-olympics-opening-ceremony-goes-viral-because-everyone-is-like-wtf-even-is-this-paris-fashion-transgender\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"[Screenshot/Public/Twitter/NBC]  Social media erupted Friday afternoon with everyone asking \\\"what the f*ck\\\" is going on at the Olympics opening ceremony?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.174311974330532e-22, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999997496306918, \"rank\": 2.301666318145296e-07, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will never forget watching the London Olympics opening ceremony in 2012.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 188, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London Olympics opening ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My family and I said we'd watch 10 minutes and go to bed.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We watched the entire thing, all three and a half hours because it was gorgeous, an absolutely magnificent tribute to Great Britain and our rich, cultural history.\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.5957649530656086, \"rank\": 0.6392549464961295, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly Paris missed the memo and decided to become the trash capital of the universe on Friday night.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999949025096, \"rank\": 5.097598304099649e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some idiot organizing the 2024 Paris Olympics opening ceremony hired a bunch of gutter-dwelling early 2000s emo clowns to reenact The Last Supper.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's not even the blasphemy that just set France back 100 years.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8321893189347471, \"rank\": 0.19395433207480947, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics Opening Ceremony Goes Viral Because WTF Even Is This?pic.twitter.com/gFcGyv2dB9  - Daily Caller (@DailyCaller)July 26, 2024    Apparently this opening ceremony at the Paris Olympics was a mocking of \\\"The Last Supper\\\".\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics began by mocking/blaspheming Christians.pic.twitter.com/Z0LwXlAoDW  - Anthony Cabassa (IWA) (@AnthonyCabassa_)July 26, 2024    What you are seeing here, ladies and gentlemen, are a bunch of dudes dressed in the ugliest outfits you have ever seen, pretending to be women, even though no self-respecting woman would be caught dead wearing a single thread seen on this stage.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not a fan of taking the Lord's name in vein, so I will let Him deal with the rest of it.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What the hell is going on at the Olympics?!\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"pic.twitter.com/vr9UjalaI0  - The Post Millennial (@TPostMillennial)July 26, 2024    Whomever these men hired to style them is blind and belongs in fashion prison.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Actually, everyone involved in whatever the heck this is needs to double check their job description, because they just embarrassed the heck out of France and themselves.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8321893189347471, \"rank\": 0.19395433207480947, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(RELATED: 'Malicious Acts' Wreak Havoc At Olympics)  As ifFranceneeded anyextrahelp inembarrassingitself, am I right?\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And seriously, ladies.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How long are we going to stand by and let a bunch of dudes parade around pretending to be one of us, when none of us would ever disrespect ourselves by wearing this much tacky crap?\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If \\\"daddy did not love me\\\" was a style, it was perfectly represented in Paris tonight.\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999949025096, \"rank\": 5.097598304099649e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wi